TDJANGOH Usage Instructions
***************************

Requirements
============

GCC > 4.4.7 with build-in GFORTRAN
ROOT > 5.34/32
LHAPDF 5.9.1 (in any case lower than LHAPDF 6.x.x)
CERNLIB (2006)

(Tested on LXPLUS and CCAGE)


Environment variables
=====================

After recovering the package, export the following variables (better in .bashrc or similar) :

  export TDJANGOH=/path/to/TDJANGOH/
  export LHAPDF5=/path/to/LHAPDF5/


Setup
=====

*** Special for CCAGE *** 
   In src/Makefile, replace $(shell cernlib) by -L/afs/in2p3.fr/cernlib/@sys/pro/lib/
   Patch correcting this problem will arrive soon :-).
*************************

To setup :
  make setup (in the root directory of the package)


Compilers and Options
=====================

To build :
  make (in the root directory of the package)


Test Program
============

To build test :
  make test (in the root directory of the package)

To launch test :
  bin/test


Contact
=======

For any problem, input, questions : nicolas.pierre@cern.ch
